gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Lakers 106, Suns 103
gameRecap.excerpt: LeBron James leads the way with 31 points, eight rebounds, 11 assists and five steals as the Lakers defeated the Suns, 106-103 and advance to the IST Semifinals to face the Pelicans. Anthony Davis added 27 points and 15 rebounds in the victory, while Kevin Durant added 31 points (12-17 FG), seven rebounds and four assists for the Suns in the losing effort. The Lakers improve to 13-9 on the season, while the Suns fall to 12-9.
